skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: rex fist bro
des: Meet Rex Fistbro, the world's strongest magic 8-ball. He just finished up an intense set at the gym, and now he's pumped to answer all of your life and/or workout questions, provided they can be answered with a yes or no answer. He'll also sometimes throw out tips to help with your own workouts, though he can be a bit of a jerk.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
